Normal
Target 1 face-up Attack Position monster you control; your opponent draws 1 card, also that monster gains 1000 ATK until the end of this turn, and if it does, it can attack up to 2 monsters during each Battle Phase this turn. If it attacks or is attacked this turn, your opponent takes no battle damage from that attack.
